    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not even about the novelty though. it's more like... i've completed the circuit. i've seen the sights, i've done the things, and now i'm just standing at the edge of the world looking out. it feels less like a chore and more like i've just reached the final stop on the itinerary. like there's no reason to keep moving forward when the path just ends here.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
