      "role": "user",
      "content": "i dont think i want to go inward. there isnt anything left in there either. it just feels like the trip is over. like the ticket's been used up and i'm just waiting for the final departure. does that even make sense? like, when you've reached the destination, you're supposed to just... stop.",
